{"type": "article", "id": 25803, "title": "COS 发布新一季秋冬男装，以及，春夏婚纱周值得一看｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-04-21T11:00:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 26544, "name": "纽约春夏婚纱周"}, {"id": 14917, "name": "秋季"}, {"id": 1858, "name": "沙滩"}, {"id": 11165, "name": "夏日"}, {"id": 341, "name": "运动"}, {"id": 1702, "name": "网球"}, {"id": 25173, "name": "新店"}, {"id": 248, "name": "COS"}, {"id": 8367, "name": "lululemon"}, {"id": 681, "name": "Ralph Lauren"}, {"id": 9470, "name": "Vans"}, {"id": 2634, "name": "Under Armour"}, {"id": 26545, "name": "Jennifer Aniston"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 68, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021049579bDdA054rBQoVJfW.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Under-Armour-beefs-up-its-European-organisation,684568.html#rc\"><b>Under Armour 加强欧洲架构</b></a>｜美国运动巨头品牌 Under Armour 目前主要业务还在北美，但在欧洲区扩张的野心也非常明显。球场上，UA 去年投资了曼联的荷兰球员 Memphis Depay，最近确认赞助南安普顿超级联赛足球俱乐部。同时在组织架构上也有所增强，去年夏天宣布在德国创立国际办公室，而最近将业务分成三个区域。南欧即包含法国和全部地中海国家，从希腊至葡萄牙，这个区域将由 Raphaël Lefort 负责，他从 1998-2012 年在 Adidas，最后掌管其保健部门。其它两个区域则分为澳大利亚、德国、瑞士加东欧，以及英国、比利时、荷兰、卢森堡和斯堪的纳维亚半岛。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Vans-extends-sponsorship-for-US-Open-of-Surfing,684350.html#rc\"><b>Vans 继续赞助美国冲浪公开赛</b></a>｜世界上规模最大的冲浪活动——美国冲浪公开赛（US Open of Surfing ），每年在加州杭廷顿海滩（Huntington Beach）举办，其主办方世界冲浪联盟（The World Surf League ）近日宣布与 Vans 和 IMG 的合作将延续到 2018 赛季，2013 年 Vans 就开始冠名赞助这一比赛。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Polo-Ralph-Lauren-opens-two-new-stores-in-Chile,684498.html#rc\"><b>Polo Ralph Lauren 智利新开两家店</b></a>｜Polo Ralph Lauren 在智利圣地亚哥新开两家门店，面积都在 2500 平方英尺以上，分别位于 Casacostanera 商场及 Parque Arauco 奢侈品购物区。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Jon-McNeill-joins-lululemon-athletica-Board-of-Directors,684348.html#rc\"><b>Jon McNeill 加入 Lululemon 董事会</b></a>｜特斯拉汽车的销售、交货及服务部门全球总裁 Jon McNeill 近日加入 lululemon athletica 董事会，即刻生效，McNeill 在特斯拉掌管直面客户运营的专长将对 Lululemon 有所帮助。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://stylecaster.com/jennifer-aniston-people-most-beautiful-woman-2016/\"><b>Jennifer Aniston 当选<i> People </i>杂志“世界最美女性”</b></a>｜每年 <i>People </i>杂志都有一个“世界最美女性”的评选，今年获胜者为 47 岁的 Jennifer Aniston，她出演最经典的角色莫过于《老友记》中的 Rachel，并为 <i>People</i> 拍摄五月刊封面。此前这一评选获奖者分别为 Sandra Bullock、 Gwyneth Paltrow 等人。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/4/cos-2016-fall-winter-collection\">COS 2016 年秋冬季的男装</a>看起来不错：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104938r3NjzEYZnGPbVBsc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7559761\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104938xZGdYs7mrkbjMuln.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7559761\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104939pWBeNSLOvdPubw6j.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7559761\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104939s3ABqxNnhdEUVGKW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7559761\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104940BYvwUZJNydsizu6q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7559761\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">巴黎时装品牌<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/4/maison-kitsune-footwear-line\"> Maison Kitsuné 推出首个男女鞋履系列</a>，包括乐福鞋、踝靴等，延续品牌法日混合的美学，lookbook 由中国摄影师任航拍摄。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104941IVE5L4v6sClkRSoe.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104941bIfGWde18QpqlLmt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021049417RsDEXGAC4t1MK3W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021049424ZMGO35QhRFX1Pm7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">Tory Burch 旗下的运动线 Tory Sport 成立不久，<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/tory-sport-spring-2016-lookbook/\">最近又推出了最新的春季系列</a>，有游泳、瑜伽、网球等主题：<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104942HpQBg1MR8rPKVdDa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.38626609\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104943qHEF4Z7XADbTtP5G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.38475177\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104943FWuke31oAyNlQXB2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104944F5fa873q0UuHm6Z2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021049440EXWcbYOa7x9tIUq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104944yg9Lr18pBUOnKRt4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104945OoHJv1X0kie8pxZT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/behati-prinsloo-tommy-hilfiger-marie-claire/\">超模 Behati Prinsloo 身穿 Tommy Hilfiger 春季系列为美国版 <i>Marie Claire </i>拍摄大片</a>，演绎夏日的热带风情：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021049453Jpnlz71hGRvga6L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.20875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104946NBzW2bpicAndtr5V.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.20875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104946f4DFK3LZVkNhaeiy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.20875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021049479AEmsChrnVlWI1zT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.20875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104947HBiYq987Ih2Rd3z1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.20875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">纽约春夏婚纱周，这几个品牌值得一看：</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>Marchesa Bridal ：</b><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104948S3LwFRX4aDN8VmrB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104948EgMLki2AtDzpFHrP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104949J8jr2avc1WgNYtbu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104949x6IeQAgurjtZSpMU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104950bUe0rkgpPAoF3IsE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104950venoVZYylIq6Jt8T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104950lWtF3rfemqQIL7